cmm5mpnsl001b2ut5ztpsayr6	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	1 3 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 Motores e Reversores 3. As válvulas de emergência para captação da água do porão (via bomba do motor BE) deve estar fechada. Figura 2 - Válvula de emergência 4. Veja se existe água dentro dos filtros sepa- radores de água (Racor) de cada motor. Se houver drene. 5. Verifique o nível de combustível nos tan- ques diários; 6. Verifique o nível de óleo lubrificante dos motores da seguinte forma: a) Ligue o motor e depois de aquecido de- ligue e aguarde 10 minutos para o óleo retornar ao cárter. b) Retire a vareta de medição e limpe-a com um pano limpo que não solte fios (NÃO USE ESTOPA). Recoloque a va- reta e retire-a em seguida para ver o nível do óleo. O óleo deve estar entre as mar- cas de MÁXIMO e MÍNIMO. Se o óleo estiver próximo da marca de MÍNIMO então complete o nível pelo bocal. Não coloque óleo além da marcação MÁXI- MO. Use óleo lubrificante Lubrax Nau- tica 15W40, ou outro óleo homologado para os motores MTU (consulta a assis- tência técnica MTU). 	13	21	[0.052749,0.049138,0.037706,0.046331,0.053551,0.034898,0.060771,0.04613,0.04613,0.046331,0.055556,0.035901,0.042921,0.048537,0.044124,0.045127,0.076415,0.044927,0.051345,0.044927,0.036904,0.032893,0.055356,0.034898,0.060169,0.072203,0.054353,0.036302,0.051545,0.050743,0.060571,0.064983,0.051345,0.062977,0.068393,0.063379,0.051345,0.048136,0.038308,0.034898,0.083435,0.052147,0.050342,0.057161,0.050342,0.066186,0.065986,0.064782,0.048938,0.051746,0.032492,0.054353,0.051345,0.049138,0.05696,0.055155,0.019254,0.059568,0.097073,0.06398,0.050342,0.065785,0.066186,0.062175,0.068393,0.0355,0.063579,0.060771,0.019254,0.088449,0.066186,0.06398,0.065384,0.046932,0.087446,0.06378,0.08885,0.049339,0.045929,0.046732,0.050943,0.032291,0.066387,0.059969,0.049941,0.063178,0.059167,0.075212,0.089051,0.048136,0.072203,0.08163,0.084438,0.043523,0.057562,0.048537,0.033093,0.066989,0.046331,0.042319,0.032291,0.045328,0.064181,0.064582,0.036302,0.094