cmm5mpo2p002z2ut5w4mxplge	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	2 8 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 MANUTENÇÃO 1. Uma vez ao mês verifique: a) Mangueiras e mangotes – sem rachadu- ras, não estrangulados e não entupidos. b) Conexões das mangueiras – bem fixas e sem vazamentos. c) Conexões elétricas da bomba do esgui- cho de âncora – bem fixas e não oxidadas. d) Fixação geral – bem firme e não oxidada. e) O estado dos anodos de zinco dos tro- cadores de calor e do riser do escapa- mento. Substitua se estiverem gastos 50% ou mais. A IM95 possui um sistema de circulação de água salgada integrado utilizado para refrigerar o estabilizador e os compressores do ar condi- cionado chiller e alimentar o dessanilizador. Esse sistema possui duas bombas, ambas são idênticas e possuem capacidade para alimentar todos os equipamentos ligados à elas. Sendo assim, durante a operação da embarcação apenas uma delas será aciona- da, a outra tem a função de backup. A refrigeração dos geradores e do sistema hidráulico dos guinchos e thrusters é feita de maneira independente. VE	28	51	[0.010488,0.009456,0.015073,0.012952,0.016964,0.010832,0.012838,0.008425,0.016391,0.009972,0.015417,0.014557,0.008368,0.013927,0.017022,0.015016,0.015531,0.014614,0.009055,0.009399,0.016277,0.010373,0.016792,0.013984,0.015933,0.014041,0.015474,0.009227,0.011176,0.005502,0.017022,0.015933,0.016563,0.018053,0.016735,0.01983,0.019314,0.022523,0.019715,0.015875,0.013984,0.01129,0.014443,0.014729,0.017194,0.017365,0.013927,0.014099,0.01811,0.020861,0.02579,0.014786,0.014041,0.017939,0.015016,0.017824,0.026249,0.017939,0.014672,0.010431,0.018397,0.01834,0.018168,0.014328,0.01811,0.018856,0.014729,0.014385,0.012666,0.005788,0.013984,0.0145,0.015073,0.019142,0.01364,0.017423,0.017595,0.019314,0.014786,0.014156,0.015818,0.009972,0.012609,0.011978,0.014614,0.007393,0.009915,0.017537,0.0145,0.018856,0.019658,0.020002,0.01834,0.013984,0.010373,0.483481,0.009456,0.019429,0.01364,0.018397,0.010316,0.018168,0.018512,0.017537,0.021033,0.0243,0