cmm5mpo5o003h2ut5tdw3s36f	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	3 4 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 ATENÇÃO! A leitura desse capítulo não substitui a leitura do manual do equipamento. A IM95 é equipada com uma unidade hi- dráulica exclusiva para o sistema de direção. Essa unidade hidráulica possui duas bombas com capacidade de operar o sistema indepen- dentemente. A bomba principal está ligada à rede elétrica AC da embarcação. A bomba auxiliar está ligada à rede elétrica DC. O piloto automático irá atuar diretamente na unidade hidráulica, ou seja, não existe uma bomba de piloto no sistema de direção. ATENÇÃO! As duas bombas nunca irão operar ao mesmo tempo. A bomba auxiliar tem a função de “back-up” do sistema. VERIFICAÇÕES 1. Verifique se as válvulas A, B, D, E, N, P; G, I, S, T e X estão abertas . 2. Verifique se as válvulas C, F, H, M, U, V estão fechadas . Figura 19 - Unidade hidráulica LIGAR 1. A direção hidráulica estará pronta a operar quando um dos motores estiver em operação. PERIGO! Se a unidade hidráulica não ligar após o acionamento do motor,	34	60	[0.014716,0.015812,0.015108,0.012837,0.018787,0.008454,0.026145,0.010646,0.018943,0.012916,0.019256,0.013855,0.011428,0.017064,0.017926,0.023248,0.0209,0.013933,0.022544,0.019256,0.022387,0.022779,0.020117,0.010254,0.016986,0.012916,0.018395,0.013151,0.020509,0.018552,0.021135,0.024266,0.016986,0.018395,0.020587,0.028336,0.023561,0.019726,0.020352,0.022544,0.02771,0.020039,0.019961,0.02043,0.020274,0.015186,0.019648,0.02317,0.028728,0.018552,0.023327,0.025675,0.025988,0.023405,0.013933,0.018395,0.02364,0.024814,0.036399,0.034599,0.027397,0.024501,0.02544,0.01816,0.024814,0.029354,0.022544,0.010724,0.02317,0.021839,0.016595,0.020665,0.021526,0.020039,0.019413,0.021839,0.018552,0.018239,0.018317,0.019569,0.024579,0.033816,0.034912,0.035381,0.020822,0.025518,0.024031,0.018082,0.024344,0.029745,0.014168,0.025675,0.02497,0.018865,0.025753,0.018004,0.024657,0.0191,0.020352,0.018787,0.020039,0.043287,0.020039,0.02043,0.025049,0.026849