cmm5mpo71003p2ut5a4mt1n90	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	3 6 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 MANUTENÇÃO 1. Uma vez ao mês , verifique: a) Conexões das tubulações – bem fixas e sem vazamentos. b) Mangueiras – não devem estar estrangu- ladas e nem danificadas. c) Fixação geral dos componentes – bem firme e não oxidada. d) Nível do reservatório do sistema. Se estiver baixo, procure por vazamentos e depois complete o nível com óleo hi- dráulico ISO VG22. 2. Siga as demais instruções de manutenção encontradas no manual do equipamento. ATENÇÃO! Só permita que profissionais autorizados fa- çam trabalhos de substituição, instalação ou reparos em partes e peças de sua embarcação. Caso isto não seja obedecido haverá a perda da Garantia da Embarcação. Direção hidráulica com piloto automático AMIGO DO MAR Todo o descarte de óleo hidráulico que cair no porão, deverá ser feito em local apropria- do. NÃO JOGUE AO MAR! As marinas de- vem ter um recipiente para estes produtos. Figura 23 - Pistão de direção	36	64	[0.014907,0.011537,0.023657,0.014259,0.014972,0.01212,0.014454,0.011343,0.010759,0.01238,0.01413,0.014,0.014194,0.015167,0.017565,0.010954,0.017889,0.011602,0.014518,0.01575,0.013352,0.016398,0.018537,0.016268,0.026639,0.011343,0.013352,0.011278,0.01737,0.016139,0.020028,0.018342,0.027416,0.035972,0.014065,0.019379,0.013676,0.026768,0.021259,0.013805,0.015685,0.016268,0.01763,0.016852,0.015102,0.020157,0.020481,0.01912,0.029361,0.020935,0.016398,0.014907,0.020417,0.015685,0.015555,0.021454,0.030074,0.022037,0.01562,0.016722,0.015167,0.021389,0.011537,0.016592,0.020481,0.01588,0.016852,0.015685,0.019768,0.026768,0.015167,0.011148,0.013157,0.014259,0.01387,0.011926,0.018213,0.016528,0.018342,0.019704,0.025213,0.017824,0.018731,0.013935,0.01575,0.01588,0.018861,0.012509,0.011667,0.018861,0.018083,0.019444,0.018861,0.026315,0.033898,0.028454,0.010759,0.016009,0.014,0.550857,0.006222,0.021259,0.019639,0.021518,0.011213,0.020935,0.02087,0.021454,0.010435,0.022361,0.016722,0.015167,0.011537,0