cmm5mpobv004h2ut52r7cq9py	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	4 6 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 Flaps eletro-hidráulicos LIGAR 1. Ligue o interruptor das baterias de serviço 24V. 2. O voltímetro DC deve estar no mínimo em 24V (painel DP1). OPERAR 1. Ambos os flap’s são acionados pelas mes- ma unidade hidráulica. Veja a posição da unidade na página seguinte. 2. A operação dos flap’s é feita por um par de botões de controle que estão nos painéis do flybridge e do salão. Figura 31 - Painel de comando flap’s 3. Conforme a distribuição de peso e ação do vento na embarcação, pequenos ajustes nos ângulos dos flap’s podem resultar num ganho de desempenho da embarcação. Figura 32 - Unidade hidráulica flap’s MANUTENÇÃO 1. Uma vez ao mês, verifique: a) Conexões das mangueiras – sem vaza- mentos. b) Mangueiras – não devem estar estrangu- ladas e nem danificadas. c) Fixação geral dos componentes – bem firme e não oxidada. d) Nível do reservatório do sistema (foto abaixo). Se estiver baixo procure o va- zamento e depois complete com fluído hidráulico ISO46. e) O e	46	78	[0.007757,0.010412,0.008587,0.007674,0.011574,0.01008,0.01174,0.0095,0.012528,0.006845,0.008379,0.006845,0.009292,0.009665,0.01232,0.003982,0.011615,0.009375,0.012445,0.0151,0.011864,0.007591,0.00867,0.008255,0.011366,0.009624,0.011988,0.007965,0.00755,0.006762,0.00672,0.00784,0.008255,0.010868,0.011076,0.00867,0.017796,0.018252,0.013357,0.010329,0.013482,0.010122,0.010744,0.012528,0.010163,0.009582,0.013482,0.01846,0.013648,0.010371,0.012611,0.013316,0.010454,0.013648,0.010412,0.01174,0.011864,0.348371,0.012279,0.008919,0.008214,0.005268,0.343849,0.005434,0.011823,0.013109,0.013026,0.010785,0.01315,0.010205,0.013523,0.007176,0.012569,0.007218,0.01315,0.009873,0.014063,0.018958,0.014187,0.010329,0.013482,0.014436,0.01344,0.015058,0.017589,0.012777,0.010122,0.007384,0.009582,0.0095,0.011159,0.009707,0.012735,0.018792,0.010246,0.01315,0.007135,0.0095,0.01792,0.015349,0.010703,0.010246,0.013067,0.01427,0.009873,0.019206,0.013689,0