cmm5mpoe3004t2ut5zdmk9zyv	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	5 0 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 Plataforma hidráulica de popa DESLIGAR 1. Desligue a chave de bateria da plataforma no painel do cockpit. MANUTENÇÃO 1. Uma vez ao mês , verifique: a) Conexões das mangueiras – bem fixas e sem vazamentos. b) Mangueiras – não devem estar estrangu- ladas e nem danificadas. c) Fixação geral dos componentes – bem firme e não oxidada. d) Os anodos da plataforma hidráulica (foto abaixo) troque-os se estiverem de- gradados 50% ou mais. e) Nível do reservatório do fluído hidráuli- co. Se estiver baixo conserte o vazamen- to se houver e depois complete com fluí- do hidráulico Tellus 46. f) Limpe e lubrifique com vaselina as partes articuladas 2. Uma vez ao ano, solicite à Assistência Téc- nica Autorizada que faça uma revisão geral. ATENÇÃO! Só permita que profissionais autorizados façam trabalhos de substituição, instalação ou reparos em partes e peças de sua embarcação. Caso isto não seja obedecido haverá a perda da Garantia da Embarcação.	50	84	[0.023551,0.014761,0.012465,0.010562,0.012333,0.024864,0.014105,0.016007,0.019615,0.024339,0.019353,0.016073,0.019878,0.014957,0.013514,0.011612,0.014564,0.015417,0.014761,0.017057,0.01955,0.011481,0.018172,0.015417,0.018434,0.016532,0.0185,0.016663,0.013383,0.010562,0.019746,0.022108,0.015745,0.021387,0.021715,0.020927,0.017516,0.022239,0.021583,0.016466,0.016007,0.020009,0.01627,0.020731,0.017122,0.029062,0.020927,0.029981,0.019878,0.021124,0.015089,0.01686,0.016138,0.01955,0.015154,0.016663,0.016466,0.020927,0.021124,0.016007,0.013121,0.01745,0.018631,0.014367,0.019878,0.014433,0.01417,0.016073,0.012137,0.012202,0.01791,0.01745,0.013449,0.028931,0.0288,0.021255,0.017319,0.011874,0.016663,0.020468,0.012333,0.016073,0.01358,0.029128,0.020927,0.028144,0.029718,0.016007,0.010759,0.021124,0.016401,0.011677,0.020534,0.020534,0.021583,0.020468,0.022699,0.020534,0.021518,0.02014,0.020665,0.020403,0.011481,0.016794,0.020009,0.021124,0.017319,0.019681,0.02132