cmm5mpoes004x2ut5omc3bx2b	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	5 2 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 Ponte hidráulica de embarque OPERAR 1. A operação é feita pelo painel do cockpit, próxima à entrada BB da embarcação (foto abaixo), ou pelo controle remoto. Figura 36 - Painel acionamento passarela 2. Quando estender a ponte observe se ela poderá bater no pier com a mudança da maré e com a ondulação gerada por algum barco. 3. Não acione a ponte se houver alguém so- bre ela. 4. Não utilize a ponte como trampolim, pois a sobrecarga momentânea poderá danificar a fixação junto ao barco. 5. Só permita que uma pessoa por vez atra- vesse a ponte. 6. Se ocorrer alguma pane elétrica na ponte, é possível movimentá-la manualmente. Atue o solenóide da válvula direcional manualmente e, então, acione a alavanca manual da bomba. Figura 37 - Unidade hidráulica ponte DESLIGAR 1. Retire os postes de proteção lateral. 2. Recolha totalmente a ponte. ATENÇÃO! A ponte hidráulica irá, automaticamen- te, ajustar sua inclinação antes de se re- colher. Esse movimento é controlado p	52	86	[0.051684,0.04909,0.03572,0.045698,0.056274,0.033325,0.059666,0.073835,0.058469,0.03552,0.081617,0.051884,0.046895,0.033724,0.054678,0.048491,0.039512,0.035121,0.058669,0.049888,0.057072,0.03572,0.028337,0.030332,0.036718,0.029334,0.042106,0.066252,0.046895,0.025742,0.055675,0.051684,0.052682,0.053879,0.047494,0.047095,0.061063,0.050487,0.060265,0.051884,0.087404,0.051884,0.065653,0.06705,0.046296,0.048092,0.048292,0.065054,0.065054,0.048691,0.049489,0.051285,0.062261,0.058868,0.050886,0.067249,0.068247,0.063857,0.050487,0.057671,0.070841,0.065453,0.060864,0.041507,0.058868,0.048691,0.039312,0.048691,0.03552,0.055276,0.050088,0.050886,0.051485,0.050287,0.051684,0.045099,0.085209,0.086007,0.061263,0.034922,0.089799,0.04929,0.061462,0.046695,0.066052,0.068447,0.087604,0.047693,0.064057,0.061263,0.048092,0.066451,0.051684,0.06246,0.045897,0.063059,0.073236,0.048891,0.063657,0.047693,0.065054,0.063258,0.03592,0.047095,0.054877,0.05