cmm5mpofi00512ut5tjlojyyp	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	5 3 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 Ponte hidráulica de embarque MANUTENÇÃO 1. Toda vez após retornar de um passeio ou viagem: quando fizer a lavagem do con- vés aproveite e lave também a ponte e suas ferragens da seguinte forma a) Estenda a ponte de maneira a ficar apa- rente o eixo de cada cilindro hidráulico. b) Lave com água doce corrente (manguei- ra e esguicho sem aplicar nenhum pano ou esponja no primeiro momento) reti- rando todo o sal e areia. c) Se necessário passe uma esponja. d) Aproveite o momento da lavagem e veja o estado geral das mangueiras e cone- xões. e) No final, recolha totalmente a ponte se não for utilizá-la. 2. Uma vez ao mês, verifique: a) Conexões das mangueiras – bem fixas e sem vazamentos. b) Mangueiras – não devem estar estrangu- ladas e nem danificadas. c) Fixação geral dos componentes – bem firme e não oxidada. d) Nível do reservatório de fluído hidráuli- co. Se estiver baixo conserte o vazamen- to se houver e depois complete com fluí- do hidráulico Tellus 46.	53	88	[0.018199,0.011456,0.012045,0.011456,0.019639,0.010801,0.018853,0.011718,0.019377,0.015711,0.018919,0.015907,0.018395,0.011063,0.018722,0.015711,0.012896,0.015776,0.020359,0.01198,0.014009,0.015187,0.014664,0.011652,0.016366,0.011063,0.018722,0.015711,0.025727,0.023567,0.019704,0.016955,0.02121,0.016889,0.016169,0.015907,0.02049,0.016562,0.019966,0.017675,0.024352,0.017217,0.019901,0.021341,0.020162,0.020948,0.011456,0.021341,0.02049,0.015842,0.021472,0.015842,0.02121,0.010539,0.552505,0.015842,0.021144,0.015318,0.015842,0.00923,0.017282,0.019442,0.019639,0.019508,0.017479,0.010212,0.021734,0.021341,0.015056,0.01905,0.015907,0.011718,0.011456,0.020555,0.020752,0.019573,0.019311,0.016169,0.021603,0.024352,0.017544,0.015515,0.0163,0.011521,0.028345,0.029393,0.017348,0.021603,0.020293,0.011783,0.021472,0.021865,0.015646,0.015907,0.020686,0.017151,0.02049,0.021341,0.01702,0.020948,0.021079,0.021014,0.016889,0.01977,0.017479,0.01171