cmm5mpoo0006f2ut5w2kzrzf1	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	6 7 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 Água servida (águas cinzas) e coleta da água de condensação do ar condicionado A IM95 possui duas caixas para armazena- gem de água servida, uma destinada à tripu- lação e outra para o restante da embarcação. O controle, monitoramento e operação des- se sistema é feito pelos painéis da Böning. Caso o tanque de água servida atinja seu vo- lume máximo de armazenamento, a rede de água doce da embarcação será interrompida até que esse tanque seja parcialmente esgo- tado. OPERAR 1. Monitore o nível dos tanques através do painel Böning no painel de comando do sa- lão (página “Water”). Figura 54 - Monitoramento tanques de água 2. O acionamento das bombas de esgota- mento dos tanques é feito pelo painel da Böning (página “Water”). Uma vez aciona- das, as bombas irão desligar automatica- mente quando o tanque estiver vazio. AVISO! A fim de que a água coletada não seja dis- pensada em locais impróprios, as bombas de esgotamento dos tanques NUNCA se- rão acionadas au	67	113	[0.01071,0.014375,0.011512,0.013631,0.015406,0.014833,0.016609,0.014432,0.015922,0.010653,0.011569,0.01386,0.016895,0.014776,0.00945,0.005498,0.014833,0.010252,0.013058,0.01323,0.016265,0.01386,0.011912,0.013115,0.016322,0.005498,0.022164,0.014261,0.022737,0.013745,0.014719,0.017353,0.018842,0.017811,0.013802,0.014432,0.017411,0.01764,0.01512,0.013631,0.017525,0.017869,0.014032,0.015177,0.024799,0.01701,0.026574,0.02457,0.018613,0.009221,0.014833,0.013631,0.019071,0.025658,0.013688,0.019243,0.014432,0.010309,0.018041,0.015062,0.017754,0.019014,0.018155,0.018556,0.01449,0.01764,0.009221,0.014203,0.016666,0.014776,0.032702,0.014432,0.018957,0.014089,0.013402,0.014146,0.018212,0.014432,0.019014,0.017926,0.014662,0.014203,0.018098,0.018155,0.020045,0.01827,0.025371,0.017468,0.014776,0.01134,0.016723,0.016093,0.008419,0.016494,0.013974,0.010194,0.015062,0.014203,0.017697,0.017926,0.018499,0.013287,0.018041,0.018785,0.013917,0.01386