cmm5mpooc006h2ut5pxxbo365	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	gua coletada não seja dis- pensada em locais impróprios, as bombas de esgotamento dos tanques NUNCA se- rão acionadas automaticamente. Sempre que possível esgote os tanques quando o primeiro alarme de nível alto for acionado. Figura 55 - Acionamento bombas de esgotamento tanques 3. A bomba caixa de água servida de eleva- ção e as bombas de coleta de condensação das máquinas de ar condicionado são con- troladas por sensores de nível. Essas bombas entram em operação automaticamente. Figura 56 - Bomba coleta condensação A/C 4. No caso de falha da bomba de esgotamen- to principal, o tanque de água servida princi- pal também pode ser esgotado utilizando a bomba do sistema de águas negras. Para isso, fecha a válvula AC01 e abra as válvulas ACI e ANI (indicadas na figura da página 70). 5. A água utilizada na banheira não será co- letada pelo tanque. Ela será descartada dire- tamente para o mar.	67	114	[0.069535,0.073055,0.066014,0.055892,0.068654,0.068875,0.055232,0.068434,0.068214,0.050391,0.071075,0.077896,0.055012,0.097261,0.098581,0.052811,0.035868,0.061833,0.056992,0.042249,0.038508,0.039608,0.058752,0.057652,0.056112,0.04555,0.036088,0.0955,0.070195,0.056992,0.071295,0.052811,0.072835,0.053911,0.055452,0.068214,0.071295,0.059192,0.069535,0.071515,0.065354,0.053691,0.054351,0.068654,0.036308,0.051711,0.069535,0.101001,0.073936,0.097921,0.071515,0.060293,0.051491,0.04665,0.074816,0.084938,0.052811,0.053691,0.057652,0.050831,0.071075,0.097921,0.052591,0.064694,0.071075,0.042249,0.036308,0.069975,0.069975,0.057652,0.064914,0.071295,0.051051,0.053691,0.074156,0.050611,0.072175,0.071295,0.053471,0.076136,0.067114,0.082077,0.09682,0.074596,0.054572,0.038508,0.058312,0.062053,0.072395,0.070195,0.054131,0.073055,0.070635,0.053911,0.088019,0.04973,0.061393,0.061173,0.065134,0.051051,0.056772,0.054351,0.050831,0.051491,0.069755,0.09704,0.056552,0.050391,0.051491,0.058532,0.057212,0.041369,0.041149,0.053911,0.057872,0.069755,0.