cmm5mpooo006j2ut5awgh4u6b	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	6 8 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 Água servida (águas cinzas) e coleta da água de condensação do ar condicionado Figura 57 - Bomba tanque água servida principal 6. Algumas marinas possuem um sistema de sucção dos dejetos orgânicos (águas cinzas e águas negras) produzidos na embarcação. Em ambos os bordos das embarcação existe um bocal que pode ser utilizado para reco- lhimento desse dejetos. MANUTENÇÃO 1. Uma vez ao mês: a) Verifique se os respiros dos tanques de água servida estão obstruídos. b) Verifique o fi ltro de odores dos respiros, troque-os quando sentir mal cheiro pelo respiro. c) Verifique as conexões elétricas das bom- bas. d) Verifique as conexões das mangueiras – bem fixas e sem vazamentos. e) Verifique a fixação das bombas, caixas e equipamentos – bem firmes e não oxi- dadas. f) Verifique as mangueiras – sem rachadu- ras, não estranguladas e nem entupidas. g) Limpe e teste o sensor de nível da caixa de água servida de elevação (foto abaixo): Figura 58 - Caixa de água servida	68	115	[0.012575,0.015129,0.017879,0.016504,0.014408,0.011789,0.014081,0.014605,0.016897,0.013819,0.017617,0.009693,0.016504,0.0093,0.02528,0.029734,0.016701,0.006287,0.015849,0.012967,0.013753,0.01061,0.014343,0.014998,0.012967,0.016373,0.016701,0.017617,0.008579,0.010544,0.02659,0.011527,0.016897,0.02731,0.016242,0.018796,0.015587,0.020499,0.01729,0.016373,0.019844,0.019582,0.011658,0.015849,0.028948,0.015718,0.022202,0.020368,0.02135,0.010937,0.021678,0.020106,0.016177,0.022726,0.020237,0.017159,0.012247,0.546468,0.016242,0.016963,0.019975,0.021874,0.016439,0.021612,0.016046,0.019386,0.016177,0.020434,0.014998,0.017355,0.024036,0.016046,0.022529,0.020368,0.016242,0.016963,0.010806,0.015849,0.027965,0.016635,0.024036,0.01991,0.021809,0.021154,0.017093,0.020237,0.028948,0.029079,0.02266,0.016046,0.019451,0.020172,0.010544,0.020499,0.017093,0.016308,0.023446,0.021743,0.015915,0.020958,0.015391,0.02063,0.021678,0.022333,0.022529,0.029