cmm5mpouu007f2ut509o5szbj	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	7 8 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 Ar-condicionado | CHILLER A seleção da bomba é feita no painel de co- mando dos compressores na casa de máqui- nas. Siga as seguintes etapas para alterar a bomba: a) No menu principal selecione a opção “G. Manufactor”. Essa seção é protegida com senha, a senha padrão do equipa- mento é 3185. b) No menu “Manufactor” selecione a op- ção “Factory Settings”. c) Navegue pelos menus até encontrar a tela representada na figura a seguir. En- tão alterne entra a bomba A ou B na op- ção “CW Pump”. Figura 65 - Seleção bomba de água doce DESLIGAR 1. Desligue todos os evaporadores sistema. 2. Desligue os compressores. No painel de comando selecione o modo off. 3. Se não for utilizar o estabilizador e o dessa- linizador, desligue a bomba de água salgada. MANUTENÇÃO 1. Alterne a bomba de água doce que irá ope- rar. Isso prolongará a vida útil das bombas. 2. Uma vez por semana: a) Verifique a pressão da rede de água doce do sistema, manômetro próximo ao tan- que de diesel	78	131	[0.348183,0.008103,0.007688,0.006773,0.009516,0.00669,0.01097,0.009641,0.012425,0.009682,0.011178,0.008103,0.008934,0.005859,0.010555,0.008768,0.010721,0.009433,0.011053,0.005901,0.015832,0.01363,0.011095,0.007521,0.009682,0.004571,0.007729,0.008851,0.016372,0.00748,0.011095,0.014045,0.010555,0.012923,0.010513,0.013422,0.010222,0.012466,0.013464,0.010222,0.012716,0.009931,0.010181,0.012508,0.013297,0.00669,0.015832,0.010347,0.011843,0.011677,0.0091,0.011511,0.012549,0.011178,0.012175,0.00748,0.011427,0.010347,0.013006,0.006856,0.013422,0.012965,0.020278,0.015001,0.013588,0.010264,0.013214,0.010638,0.00669,0.010139,0.012674,0.010596,0.010763,0.009557,0.008643,0.019323,0.010472,0.013588,0.007438,0.010347,0.012425,0.013214,0.007688,0.010513,0.014004,0.015043,0.013297,0.010098,0.017744,0.010389,0.013048,0.010015,0.01097,0.01309,0.012549,0.00669,0.009641,0.019572,0.011511,0.01043,0.013048,0.00669,0.012757,0.009516,0.013464,0.007272