cmm5mpov8007h2ut5ctzfyms8	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	. 2. Uma vez por semana: a) Verifique a pressão da rede de água doce do sistema, manômetro próximo ao tan- que de diesel diário de bombordo. A pressão deve estar entre 15-20psi. 3. Uma vez ao mês verifique a) Mangueiras – sem rachaduras, não es- tranguladas ou entupidas. b) Conexões das mangueiras – bem fixas e sem vazamentos. c) Conexões elétricas das bombas – bem fixas e não oxidadas. d) Fixação das bombas e filtros – bem fir- mes e não oxidadas. e) Drenos das bandejas coletoras da água de condensação – não entupidos. f) Bombas de coletada de condensação dos evaporadores – teste o funcionamento. g) Filtro porta manta (branca) da entrada de ar fresco do sistema, na primeira cai- xa BB do solário. Troque a manta a cada três meses. 4. A cada seis meses: a) Troque o filtro de odor de carvão sob o filtro porta manta AVISO! Consulte a assistência técnica Intermari- ne para saber onde adquirir os filtros de reposição.	78	132	[0.012145,0.011715,0.012623,0.012528,0.00526,0.010902,0.011524,0.011476,0.008081,0.014153,0.015397,0.017022,0.011476,0.017931,0.020943,0.015588,0.00459,0.015588,0.014249,0.016018,0.011619,0.011476,0.014727,0.012815,0.007746,0.01401,0.012097,0.008511,0.014584,0.017214,0.015636,0.011571,0.01554,0.015875,0.01554,0.012432,0.015636,0.00459,0.402128,0.008081,0.015205,0.015827,0.015492,0.012336,0.011906,0.02123,0.016066,0.009133,0.011858,0.014488,0.00789,0.016162,0.010998,0.014871,0.011906,0.011428,0.017166,0.013245,0.007172,0.019557,0.014632,0.014392,0.010998,0.007698,0.012767,0.015253,0.015492,0.012528,0.008655,0.014775,0.012815,0.00789,0.01028,0.01511,0.011858,0.015444,0.015636,0.016209,0.011189,0.012384,0.011715,0.0219,0.011428,0.014679,0.021326,0.01511,0.011141,0.015923,0.02166,0.014679,0.012289,0.011906,0.014918,0.021565,0.012432,0.013341,0.016018,0.016162,0.01181,0.014727,0.016018,0.007698,0.015779,0.014297,0.008942,0.01444,0.011715,0.015827,0.011763,0.011715,0.01095,0.015062,0.010998,0.007794,0.015