cmm5mporg006x2ut5oxgqlz8g	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	7 3 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 Sistema de esgoto (águas negras) | VASOS SANITÁRIOS 6. Algumas marinas possuem um sistema de sucção dos dejetos orgânicos (águas cinzas e águas negras) produzidos na embarcação. Em ambos os bordos das embarcação existe um bocal que pode ser utilizado para reco- lhimento desse dejetos. Vasos sanitários 1. Os vasos sanitários estarão prontos para utilização quando a luz central do painel es- tiver acesa (figura abaixo). Se a luz estiver apagada, verifique se o tanque de águas ne- gras não está cheio. 2. Antes de utilizar os vasos sanitários pres- sione o botão à esquerda do painel (“BEFO- RE USE”) para encher a cuba. Figura 62 - Painel de controle vasos sanitários 3. Após o uso, pressione o botão à direita (“AFTER USE”) para esvaziar a cuba. ATENÇÃO! Nunca jogue no vaso sanitário: papel higiênico, absorventes, preservativos, pedaços de cigarros, produtos químicos ou qualquer outro material estranho às funções deste equipamento. MANUTENCÃO 1. Quando o barco n	73	122	[0.022456,0.020446,0.015851,0.005513,0.016253,0.010395,0.015736,0.014875,0.016196,0.013784,0.008442,0.009247,0.01028,0.012865,0.015105,0.013324,0.017,0.018723,0.015047,0.010051,0.012692,0.012865,0.01677,0.014358,0.011486,0.013152,0.011486,0.009763,0.015851,0.013324,0.017517,0.018148,0.014243,0.019182,0.014013,0.013899,0.018953,0.009993,0.014186,0.018838,0.009706,0.019182,0.017976,0.01878,0.014243,0.018895,0.024983,0.014186,0.014932,0.024868,0.011084,0.010855,0.017861,0.018206,0.014186,0.018838,0.018551,0.013324,0.014358,0.017172,0.018148,0.013956,0.021307,0.020331,0.014243,0.01298,0.01275,0.009132,0.011142,0.016138,0.009304,0.016942,0.011946,0.01723,0.017689,0.017632,0.01924,0.017172,0.016598,0.017804,0.013324,0.010453,0.015334,0.015736,0.009476,0.015909,0.018436,0.018034,0.019412,0.017402,0.017976,0.018206,0.011142,0.014473,0.018953,0.014875,0.014415,0.01878,0.01723,0.018378,0.013899,0.026419,0.018551,0.015047,0.015047,0.0182