cmm5mpos900712ut5k1f9jv2e	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	7 4 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 Sistema de esgoto (águas negras) | VASOS SANITÁRIOS 4. Uma vez ao semestre ou antes e após a temporada de maior uso da embarcação, limpe com água doce e cloro o sistema: a) Leve a embarcação para águas abertas, esvazie o tanque de esgoto, depois dê a descarga por 3 vezes em cada vaso sani- tário e então esvazie novamente o tan- que de esgoto. b) Jogue 1 ml de cloro (aproximadamente o volume de uma colher de café) para cada descarga. Repita esta operação em todos os vasos até atingir 10% da capaci- dade do tanque de esgoto. c) Complete o tanque com uma solução de cloro na proporção de 1ml de cloro (aproximadamente o volume de uma co- lher de café) para cada 10 litros. Utilize o bocal de sucção para tal. d) Espere uma hora e então esvazie o tan- que. e) Dê descarga, em todos os vasos, usando apenas água doce até atingir 10% da ca- pacidade do tanque. f) Complete o tanque com água doce pelo bocal de sucção. g) E finalmente esvazie o tanque de esgoto. PERIGO! 	74	124	[0.027868,0.033811,0.056556,0.052868,0.041392,0.052048,0.058195,0.033811,0.044056,0.051433,0.043442,0.053687,0.059425,0.035655,0.033196,0.032991,0.059425,0.053892,0.060244,0.040573,0.043032,0.049589,0.044261,0.033606,0.04795,0.076842,0.038933,0.049589,0.055326,0.050818,0.043851,0.064138,0.053482,0.069056,0.063318,0.053482,0.050409,0.049589,0.063523,0.033811,0.050818,0.064138,0.050613,0.067826,0.068646,0.050204,0.052048,0.050409,0.037499,0.092416,0.062294,0.068236,0.065982,0.053687,0.036065,0.049794,0.051228,0.064957,0.063113,0.063318,0.091801,0.039548,0.019672,0.068236,0.049384,0.061679,0.055736,0.043442,0.060039,0.043442,0.073154,0.05799,0.043851,0.056351,0.042212,0.061269,0.08258,0.056966,0.059015,0.043851,0.056761,0.039753,0.064957,0.032786,0.04713,0.064138,0.065367,0.066187,0.04754,0.052253,0.064752,0.055122,0.040368,0.049589,0.036884,0.03586,0.067007,0.061269,0.052253,0.060859,0.090776,0.079506,0.052663,0.050204,0.04713,0