cmm5mpotr00792ut5cn722pww	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	7 7 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 Ar-condicionado | CHILLER A IM95 é equipada com um sistema de ar condicionado chiller. O sistema é formado por três compressores, lo- calizados na casa de máquinas, e por evaporado- res espalhados pelos ambientes da embarcação. A cabine da tripulação possui máquinas self- -contained, independentes da rede chiller. ATENÇÃO! A leitura desse capítulo não substitui a leitura do manual do equipamento. LIGAR 1. Ligue a bomba de água salgada de refrigera- ção dos compressores (painel Altas principal). 2. Ligue os evaporadores dos ambientes em que deseja utilizar o ar condicionado (foto abaixo). Figura 63 - Painel ar condicionado chiller \\ ATENÇÃO! Se a bomba de água salgada não estiver ligada os evaporadores irão operar, mas apenas irão circular o ar do ambiente. OPERAR O ar condicionado pode tanto esfriar, quan- do esquentar os ambientes. Esses dois mo- dos de operação são controlados pelos com- pressores, que irão esfriar ou esquentar a rede de água doce do sis	77	128	[0.05684,0.036612,0.050974,0.050974,0.06129,0.047737,0.062908,0.051985,0.057851,0.036005,0.040051,0.035398,0.044905,0.046524,0.059874,0.03641,0.057042,0.051985,0.04268,0.032567,0.057042,0.048749,0.04349,0.048951,0.055828,0.052187,0.055626,0.035398,0.039039,0.028926,0.049558,0.059469,0.032162,0.053603,0.061897,0.05239,0.057447,0.050367,0.059267,0.066347,0.049356,0.064526,0.065538,0.064931,0.051985,0.034185,0.060481,0.042478,0.050367,0.049962,0.050974,0.042074,0.047737,0.029735,0.045715,0.044299,0.054615,0.047737,0.044905,0.059469,0.037624,0.052592,0.03641,0.089406,0.035398,0.062908,0.065942,0.063919,0.050771,0.064122,0.059672,0.04976,0.074033,0.03378,0.066549,0.06574,0.048142,0.051985,0.05239,0.050367,0.047535,0.065335,0.04794,0.063313,0.053199,0.063515,0.066145,0.046524,0.051783,0.064122,0.060683,0.052592,0.047333,0.066347,0.050165,0.049558,0.061694,0.053401,0.046524,0.089204,0.086372,0.065942,0.05239,0.062908,0.065335,0.0527