cmm5mpox1007r2ut5pz3wxf3v	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	8 3 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 Extintor automático de incêndio ATENÇÃO! A leitura desse capítulo não substitui a leitura do manual do equipamento. Figura 67 - Cilindro de combate a incêndio automático A casa de máquinas da IM95 é equipada com um sistema de combate a incêndio au- tomatizado. Esse sistema é formado por dois cilindros e diversos sensores de temperatura dispersos pelo ambiente. A ativação do sistema ocorre, automaticamen- te, por temperatura ou manualmente através dos cabos de acionamento do sistema. Quando ativado, o sistema irá, automaticamente, fechar as entradas e saídas de ar da casa de máquinas, desligar os motores, geradores, ventiladores e exaustores e liberar o gás contido nos cilindros. LIGAR 1. Verifique a pressão de gás nos cilindros e nos sensores de temperatura remotos sobre os motores (foto abaixo). Figura 68 - Sensor de temperatura remoto 2. Remova o pino de proteção para liberar o acionamento manual do sistema. A embarca- ção é entregue com o pino ativado, 	83	137	[0.053082,0.032328,0.053082,0.048692,0.059468,0.03592,0.058669,0.03572,0.0451,0.042306,0.042306,0.048492,0.059667,0.050288,0.045299,0.045698,0.079224,0.058071,0.061663,0.032927,0.056275,0.050887,0.042106,0.052084,0.05408,0.052483,0.057871,0.04929,0.051685,0.032128,0.042904,0.066252,0.064656,0.065255,0.067849,0.068048,0.065255,0.037916,0.03572,0.060864,0.066252,0.069046,0.064456,0.049889,0.086408,0.069246,0.048292,0.061264,0.063658,0.051286,0.062261,0.064856,0.035521,0.050288,0.051485,0.047893,0.075831,0.050488,0.065454,0.065255,0.051286,0.032128,0.055676,0.056275,0.056474,0.061862,0.082017,0.069844,0.044301,0.03612,0.043703,0.056674,0.046297,0.051286,0.065055,0.063658,0.03592,0.055876,0.053281,0.047694,0.038714,0.045698,0.05827,0.064856,0.065055,0.065055,0.051685,0.06266,0.032128,0.061663,0.090598,0.052284,0.065853,0.065255,0.090399,0.051685,0.048492,0.088004,0.063658,0.052483,0.052683,0.065853,0.05827,0.048891,0.068048,0.0640