cmm5mpp36008p2ut5cslggc8y	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	9 6 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 Conservação | GELCOAT E FIBRA DE VIDRO ATENÇÃO! 9. Nunca deixe água no porão da embar- cação. Seque com panos e esponja onde for possível. Deixe o porão ventilado até secar a umidade. Esta umidade é a prin- cipal causadora das degradações de ma- teriais e odores desagradáveis. ATENÇÃO! 10. O uso de capas para cobrir o convés e os fechamentos do flybridge e popa, tornam a embarcação numa estufa se não houver uma ventilação adequada. O calor acumulado sob estas proteções du- rante o dia, gera vapor d’água que fica retido dentro da embarcação. Este vapor sofre o processo de condensação durante a noite e a água condensada fica acumu- lada principalmente nos cantos das jun- ções das peças (locais com acabamento de silicone modificado). Este ambiente é favorável à proliferação de fungos. Para evitar os fungos e odores desagra- dáveis é importante que haja uma ampla ventilação das áreas internas e externas todos os dias (desde que não esteja cho- vendo). Retire t	96	154	[0.020355,0.018127,0.011949,0.020456,0.022279,0.026329,0.029367,0.017823,0.028152,0.018734,0.020152,0.02562,0.029772,0.025924,0.030684,0.023291,0.020861,0.030076,0.021367,0.01681,0.027443,0.026228,0.029064,0.024608,0.041317,0.025215,0.025823,0.03757,0.031595,0.037165,0.013266,0.033722,0.034532,0.033924,0.030988,0.025418,0.032507,0.031696,0.046684,0.044659,0.044962,0.036051,0.027038,0.018127,0.027545,0.020456,0.022076,0.040102,0.031089,0.020962,0.029469,0.025722,0.030481,0.019848,0.020557,0.027038,0.019747,0.031696,0.027443,0.016304,0.020355,0.030886,0.024101,0.031595,0.028962,0.029064,0.022481,0.029064,0.038279,0.03281,0.030076,0.022076,0.028861,0.040709,0.041216,0.031089,0.018431,0.023291,0.019139,0.025722,0.018025,0.02238,0.031393,0.024608,0.031696,0.022886,0.024304,0.031595,0.033418,0.023696,0.032405,0.031798,0.024912,0.03838,0.025519,0.032912,0.042431,0.025317,0.032608,0.025114,0.026532,0.025823,0.04476,0.018025,0.043848,0