cmm5mppci00a32ut5z9rn8tbn	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	1 0 5 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 Ao navegar PERIGO! 1. O piloto deve conduzir a embarcação em velocidade que permita manter o ple- no controle da dirigibilidade e reagir se- guramente a qualquer fato inesperado. A segurança e integridade (de sua em- barcação e passageiros, banhistas, passa- geiros das embarcações vizinhas) devem prevalecer no momento de adequar a velocidade do barco. As conseqüências produzidas pelas ondas geradas por sua embarcação são de responsabilidade do proprietário / comandante. AMIGO DO MAR 2. As ondas que um barco produz ao nave- gar planando, são prejudiciais à fauna e flora de mangues e beiras de canais. Quando se aproximar destes locais, diminua a velocida- de para abaixo do planeio. 3. A estabilidade da embarcação é fortemen- te afetada pela ação das ondas e do vento. Recomende aos passageiros que se movam com cuidado e utilizem os corrimãos para maior segurança. 4. Sempre fique atento às luzes indicadoras, alarmes, instrumentos, bússola e piloto au- tomáti	105	179	[0.038496,0.033283,0.042907,0.052731,0.036491,0.046315,0.05634,0.034887,0.061152,0.046917,0.061152,0.07639,0.067167,0.047919,0.082606,0.072982,0.057142,0.035889,0.039498,0.04832,0.062355,0.035087,0.056942,0.051929,0.06015,0.046917,0.056942,0.03228,0.054736,0.019248,0.053132,0.048922,0.041102,0.065363,0.049724,0.050526,0.064962,0.067969,0.049523,0.046516,0.058947,0.049523,0.046917,0.058546,0.058546,0.05614,0.056741,0.053734,0.059147,0.019448,0.04832,0.054335,0.055137,0.019248,0.061353,0.049323,0.064962,0.050526,0.061353,0.064761,0.063157,0.062756,0.05213,0.062155,0.062756,0.07639,0.08842,0.05213,0.046516,0.051729,0.090626,0.062556,0.03629,0.066365,0.063558,0.052932,0.048721,0.061553,0.035889,0.062556,0.066365,0.063558,0.048922,0.062155,0.062957,0.061553,0.088019,0.086014,0.062355,0.04812,0.046716,0.062355,0.019248,0.067167,0.065764,0.049122,0.066365,0.063759,0.067769,0.062756,0.06416,0.047518,0.062756,0.052731,0.074185,0.06616