cmm5mppfh00aj2ut5btbt7g5x	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	1 0 9 I N T E R M A R I N E 9 5 Ao recolher a embarcação para o seco 1. Desembarque antes todos os passageiros e convidados. 2. Observe se as antenas dos rádios VHF precisarão ser abaixadas. 3. Verifique se o “berço” de vante da carre- ta está posicionado junto à marca específica pintada no casco. 4. É recomendável marcar no casco as po- sições em que as cintas, do travel lift de sua marina, devem ser colocadas. 5. Após o término do garageamento, vá ao porão e verifique o estado geral dos moto- res, gerador, equipamentos, mangueiras, co- nexões, vazamentos e se o porão está com água salgada ou doce. 6. Confira o estado geral externo do casco e seus componentes : entradas e saídas de água, sensores do velocímetro e sonda, héli- ces, eixos, anodos, flaps, lemes e bow / stern thrusters se houver. ATENÇÃO! 7. Siga as instruções de manutenção e limpeza que estão neste manual nas Se- ções específicas de cada Sistema e tam- bém nas Seções referentes à conservação dos materiais.	109	187	[0.021721,0.012445,0.013991,0.013372,0.019479,0.019865,0.022957,0.01345,0.01716,0.008348,0.017856,0.01917,0.020948,0.020407,0.022648,0.013372,0.017392,0.019402,0.021643,0.020329,0.017701,0.019092,0.02203,0.019634,0.023498,0.012599,0.021721,0.01801,0.014377,0.019402,0.016232,0.013991,0.018242,0.019943,0.013759,0.017392,0.018938,0.03146,0.023962,0.016155,0.022648,0.025663,0.032851,0.02659,0.018861,0.013372,0.020175,0.020484,0.018629,0.016387,0.024658,0.024194,0.017469,0.028291,0.032542,0.026281,0.012445,0.024735,0.023808,0.025199,0.02489,0.019092,0.026127,0.029296,0.036407,0.019015,0.019015,0.020175,0.027595,0.014068,0.013527,0.019479,0.015228,0.024967,0.026513,0.025585,0.033779,0.024658,0.027827,0.034166,0.019788,0.020638,0.023421,0.013759,0.023962,0.024503,0.025508,0.025199,0.02574,0.019711,0.018938,0.019634,0.018938,0.025431,0.025585,0.013914,0.023885,0.025508,0.02002,0.028677,0.02404,0.01917,0.026204,0.022803,0.025199,0.019247,0.023653,0.