cmm5mppsb00c92ut58mpreg0m	cmm5mpl7e00032ut599t7cdqn	primer específico para metais, posteriormente primer para adesão da tinta e por último tinta de preferêancia a base de PU Escovado Inicialmente enxaguar com água removendo sal, areia e agentes abrasivos. Depois, com uma flanela retire toda a poeira, sal e areia da superfície, além de retirar a sujeira dos cantos e brechas. A flanela deve estar limpa e seca preferencialmente evite que solte fiapos. Verifique se há riscos e arranhões. O vinagre é um dos melhores produ- tos para ser utilizado na limpeza do aço escovado. Em um balde misture 1 litro de água morna com 1 xícara de vinagre branco, mergulhe um pano limpo nessa mistura, torça-o e passe sobre a superfície no mínimo duas vezes. Esse procedimento pode deixar fiapos, então após feito, lustre o objeto com um pano limpo e seco novamente. Por último passe óleo mineral puro para dar brilho, protege da absorção da sujeira e marcas de impressões digitais. Re- faça esses procedimentos a cada duas semanas, assim manterá à superfície conserv	116	218	[0.067468,0.063179,0.032954,0.065519,0.060254,0.064739,0.050504,0.045629,0.049724,0.062204,0.061424,0.060059,0.089698,0.047774,0.062594,0.034514,0.050309,0.042704,0.060839,0.062789,0.048944,0.060254,0.048359,0.066299,0.061424,0.063569,0.044849,0.064349,0.064739,0.034514,0.035489,0.071953,0.043484,0.066299,0.065324,0.048359,0.090283,0.063179,0.066688,0.048944,0.062204,0.047579,0.046604,0.066688,0.060839,0.047579,0.065714,0.062204,0.074488,0.088333,0.063179,0.050894,0.034124,0.043484,0.046409,0.065714,0.060839,0.047384,0.060059,0.058499,0.062984,0.048359,0.072343,0.089893,0.034709,0.063959,0.046409,0.034319,0.061034,0.064349,0.062789,0.035099,0.059669,0.044849,0.062984,0.032759,0.062594,0.066104,0.062399,0.049724,0.075268,0.064544,0.053429,0.048359,0.062594,0.066688,0.036659,0.051479,0.062789,0.063179,0.064739,0.031394,0.047579,0.057329,0.048164,0.044069,0.047189,0.067078,0.061034,0.064349,0.070978,0.089308,0.089893,0.045629,0.